headline: EVgo (EVGO) Builds Momentum in Clean Transportation Solutions
summary: EVgo Inc. (NASDAQ:EVGO) is one of the best alternative energy stocks to invest in according to analysts. On January 27, EVgo Inc. (NASDAQ:EVGO) said it plans to roll out North American Charging Standard, or NACS, connectors across its network.
